item.title: Online Web CES Data Exploration
item.description: GitHub Link : https://github.com/huangm50/cesrrrrr Abstract Data analysis on the 2019 CES Online Web Survey data. We explored the relationship between three variables that I am interested in, and found French speakers had taken more time on the survey compared to English speakers; elderly participants in the survey that speak English tend to take less time as age increases. Introduction The data is from 2019 Canadian Election Study, specifically we used the 2019 CES Online Web Survey data to investigate anything interesting about the data.
